 |title        = Torontoist Remembers: Aeroquay One
 |first        = Marc
 |last         = Lostracco
 |publisher    = Ink Truck Media
 |work         = Torontoist
 |date         = October 12, 2006
 |url          = http://torontoist.com/2006/10/torontoist_reme/
 |accessdate   = January 9, 2012
 |archive-date = 2021-08-02
 |archive-url  = https://web.archive.org/web/20210802213920/https://torontoist.com/2006/10/torontoist_reme/
}}</ref>，公路廳在機場東面興建一條四線高速公路，南起401號公路和倫科夫徑（{{lang|en|Renforth Drive}}），北至機場道/迪臣道。此道路取名“多倫多機場高速公路”（{{lang|en|Toronto Airport Expressway}}），於1964年1月3日通車<ref name="ape">{{cite report

 | title     = Annual Report
