=== 長短途行車線分流 ===
公路廳於1963年宣佈擴濶401號公路，並仿效[[芝加哥|芝加哥]]的丹賴仁高速公路（{{lang|en|Dan Ryan Expressway}}），在401號公路設立長短途行車線分流系統<ref name="FtF94">Shragge p. 94</ref>。當局其後亦研究將該設計應用於27號公路介乎QEW和401號公路之間的路段，以及QEW介乎27號公路和皇家約克道（{{lang|en|Royal York Road}}）之間的路段，並於1966年10月13日向怡陶碧谷議會展示計劃<ref>{{cite report

 | title     = Annual Report
 | publisher = Department of Highways
 | date      = March 31, 1967
 | section   = Chronology
 | page      = 315}}</ref>；設計工序則於1967年5月完成<ref name="fpr">{{cite report
 | title     = Functional Planning Report - Highway 27 Reconstruction from Dundas Street to Rexdale Boulevard and Proposed Belfield Expressway from Islington Avenue to New Highway 27
 | author    = Planning Branch
 | publisher = Ontario Department of Highways
 | date      = May 1967}}</ref>。

工程於1968年9月展開，當中包括改建27號公路與QEW及401號公路的交匯處<ref name="interchanges">{{cite news

 | title     = Drivers Face Three More Years of QE-27-401 Motoring Misery
 | work      = The Toronto Star
 | date      = July 22, 1969
 | page      = 43}}</ref>。QEW交匯處佔地{{convert|48.5|ha|acre|0}}，包括19座新建橋樑，新建路段長度相當於{{convert|42|km|mi}}長的雙程道路<ref name="interchanges" />；401號公路交匯處則佔地{{convert|156|ha|acre|0}}，包括28座新建橋樑，新建路段長度相當於{{convert|46.6|km|0|abbr=on}}長的雙程道路，成為加拿大規模最大的交匯處<ref name=globe19691120>{{cite news

 | title     = A New Maze in the Making for Motorists
 | work      = The Globe and Mail
 | location  = Toronto
 | date      = November 20, 1969
 | volume    = 126
 | issue     = 37,427
 | page      = 43}}</ref><!-- Good luck finding a more recent source -->。前者於1969年11月14日開通<ref>{{cite news

 | title     = QE and 27 Interchange Opens Friday
 | work      = The Toronto Star
 | date      = November 13, 1969
 | page      = 1}}</ref>；後者分開數階段興建，當中數條引道於1971年11月率先開通，而整個交匯處則於同年12月4日全面開通<ref>{{cite news

 | title     = 2 Ramps Opened at 27-401
 | work      = The Toronto Star
 | date      = November 24, 1971
 | page      = 1}}</ref>。27號公路介乎QEW和401號公路之間的路段亦隨之改編為427號公路<ref name="assumed">{{cite news

 | title     = Highway 27 Interchange Fully in Service
 | work      = The Globe and Mail
 | location  = Toronto
 | date      = December 4, 1971
 | volume    = 128
 | issue     = 38,061
 | page      = 5}}</ref>。此外，機場高速公路的走線亦全面改建並成為427號公路的一部份；427號公路自此以機場道/迪臣道為北端終點，在此匯入印第安線（{{lang|en|Indian Line}}）<ref name="fpr" /><ref>{{cite map

 | title       = Ontario Road Map
 | cartography = Photogrammetry Office
 | publisher   = Ministry of Transportation and Communications
 | year        = 1973
 | inset       = Metropolitan Toronto}}</ref>。

